If this sounds like a fit for you, we encourage you to apply below or send us an email at info@owproperties.com.

WHAT OUR RESIDENTS THINK
I love this community. The new owners are GREAT!! Very affordable rent. They have different ways that you can pay your rent. Very quiet and peaceful community.
- SCOTT H.
I visited my daughter there. It was very clean and well kept. The price is very reasonable. The manager was very nice. Well kept secret. I didn't even know this place existed.
- PATRICA T.
Very quiet community filled with families, older adults, and military. The rent is the cheapest in town. They usually fix things within a day. I am a very happy resident.
- CHRIS T.
Very quiet and well kept communities. After new management came in, they successfully cleaned up the property.
Park management keeps common areas in good shape and responds to residents' concerns.
Just moved here and was the best decision made. Management made our move so easy and she was very accommodating. Our neighbors are friendly and welcoming. We have been here almost 2 full weeks and are loving every minute of it.
The park-like surroundings are great for walking and golf cart evening rides. An ordinary day might include breakfast and lunch on the patio, a dip in the pool, a quick 5-minute run to the grocery store, a walk around the lake, and an afternoon visit with a neighbor.
- LISA B.
- LAURIE F.
- MARSHA P.

ABOUT OAK WOOD
REDEFINING MANUFACTURED HOUSING
We strive to make quality living both affordable and accessible, creating welcoming and friendly neighborhoods that residents are proud to live in. Whether you're looking to buy a home, secure a long-term rental, or find the ideal spot for your manufactured home, our dedicated team is here to help you every step of the way.
ROOTED IN EXCELLENCE
Welcome to Oak Wood Properties, where our commitment to excellence runs deep like the roots of an oak tree. We believe in going beyond the norm. From the moment you step into one of our communities, you'll feel the difference. It's in the details, the dedication, and the determination to create spaces that feel like home.
Well-Kept Grounds
We strive to design and maintain pleasing environments that enhance the quality of life for our residents. From landscaped grounds to well-maintained homes, every detail is considered to create a visually appealing place to call home.
Friendly Atmosphere
We foster a friendly and inclusive atmosphere where neighbors know each other by name and support one another. Our goal is to create neighborhoods where residents feel truly connected and valued.
Affordable Living
We are committed to providing affordable housing solutions without compromising on quality. By offering competitive pricing and flexible financial options, we make it possible for more people to enjoy the benefits of a comfortable home at a great price.
